trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref>, specifying the concrete MIME type for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref> to which the `MimePart` applies.
For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> class.

Gets the collection of MIME extensibility elements for the part of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref> of which the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> is a member.
This collection must have at least one member.
If it has more than one member, the members are alternative MIME formats for the current <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart>.
Members can be of the following types:
Each of these classes exposes a `Part` property specifying the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart> with which the `MimePart` is associated.
If this collection has no members, the XML Web service will fail to generate a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) file when it is requested.
For more information about how MIME extends WSDL, see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
A collection of service description format extension.
